sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the Russell 3000 index, there is noteworthy activity today in GrubHub Inc (Symbol: GRUB), where a total volume of 8,453 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 845,300 underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 46% of GRUB's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 1.8 million shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $45 strike call option expiring January 19, 2018 , with 6,505 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 650,500 underlying shares of GRUB.

Especially high volume was seen for the $77.50 strike put option expiring January 19, 2018 , with 5,029 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 502,900 underlying shares of CRM.
